<div class="post top clearfix" >
    <h2 class="title">
        <a href="http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2"><span>About Aaron  </span></a>
    </h2>

        
                    <div id="post" class="hasSidebar clearfix">
            <p>Aaron was born June 15, 1982.  He was a computer technician for Computers Plus in Lexington, KY and held a Bachelor&#8217;s degree in Construction Management.  Aaron lived his life quickly, not holding on to many things and always with a vigor to have experiences not possessions.</p>
<p>He was incredibly sentimental, though he always tried to hide it.  The small things people did for him are what touched him the most.  He was generous with the limited means he had, and his last wishes were that any money he had be given freely in ways that would impact those who received it.</p>
<p><span class='st_facebook_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='facebook'></span><span st_via='AaronCollinsOrg' st_username='AaronCollinsOrg' class='st_twitter_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='twitter'></span><span class='st_email_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='email'></span><span class='st_sharethis_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='sharethis'></span><span class='st_fblike_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='fblike'></span><span class='st_plusone_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='plusone'></span><span class='st_pinterest_hcount' st_title='About Aaron' st_url='http://aaroncollins.org/?page_id=2' displayText='pinterest'></span></p>        </div>
