        <p>Karen, I don&#8217;t know who reported that Aaron died of cancer but it certainly isn&#8217;t true.  Unfortunately, some news outlets aren&#8217;t very responsible and they report things without verifying them.  No one in the family has ever told anyone that Aaron died of cancer, so I&#8217;m unsure where they got that idea from.</p>

